<sect2>
<title>Installation of <application>gmp</application></title>

<para>Install <application>gmp</application> by running the following commands:
</para>

<screen><userinput><command>./configure --prefix=/usr --mandir=/usr/share/man --infodir=/usr/share/info &amp;&amp;
make &amp;&amp;
make install</command></userinput></screen>

</sect2>

